content:
There is an element exampleCanonical
e.g.
<exampleCanonical value="http://www.fhir.org/guides/test3/StructureDefinition/template-basic"/>

does the IG-Build use this to create a temporary fragment example list per profile? I looked and did not see anything and just wanted to confirm before creating my own script to do this.
Yes. In SDC/temp/pages, look at pages.json and search for the sdc-questionnaire profile
